<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:20:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>国际货币基金组织/世界银行会议上争夺发展资金的斗争愈演愈烈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/battle-development-cash-heats-up-imfworld-bank-meetings-2024-04-18/</link><description>本周聚集在华盛顿的发展机构面临着多年来最艰难的战斗之一：让富裕国家担心国外战争和国内选举，从而向世界上最贫穷的国家投入更多资金。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 12:13:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/battle-development-cash-heats-up-imfworld-bank-meetings-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>达能首席财务官表示，中国是主要增长动力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-sees-china-key-growth-driver-cfo-says-2024-04-18/</link><description>达能周四表示，由于医疗营养品和饮料品类依然强劲，中国仍将是这家全球最大酸奶制造商的主要增长动力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:52:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/danone-sees-china-key-growth-driver-cfo-says-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾与新西兰签署协议，共同关注南海问题</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-eye-forces-deal-share-concern-over-south-china-sea-2024-04-18/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯和新西兰总理克里斯托弗·卢克森周四同意深化防务合作，并对菲律宾和中国在南海发生海上冲突的问题表示严重关切。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:51:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-new-zealand-eye-forces-deal-share-concern-over-south-china-sea-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>英国将审查某些对外投资是否损害国家安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britain-examine-whether-some-outward-investment-undermines-national-security-2024-04-18/</link><description>英国副首相苏纳克表示，英国将审查对外投资和出口的控制，以保护其经济安全，并警告全球经济容易受到俄罗斯和中国等国家行动的影响。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:45:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/britain-examine-whether-some-outward-investment-undermines-national-security-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称瑞银关闭部分中国私募基金并将裁员</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-shuts-some-china-private-funds-will-lay-off-staff-sources-say-2024-04-18/</link><description>三位直接了解情况的消息人士称，瑞银正在关闭部分中国私募基金业务，并将裁员三分之一的员工，以削减在华运营成本。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:42:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-shuts-some-china-private-funds-will-lay-off-staff-sources-say-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲的福维亚正在与更多希望在欧洲设立工厂的中国汽车制造商进行洽谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-forvia-talking-more-chinese-automakers-looking-set-up-europe-2024-04-18/</link><description>汽车零部件供应商Forvia周四表示，正在与另外两家中国汽车制造商进行谈判，寻求扩大在欧洲的生产，以减少对中国比亚迪的依赖。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 11:27:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/europes-forvia-talking-more-chinese-automakers-looking-set-up-europe-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>宁夏化工厂爆炸造成两人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/two-killed-explosion-chemical-plant-chinas-ningxia-2024-04-18/</link><description>据官方媒体新华社周四报道，中国西北部宁夏地区一家化工厂发生爆炸，造成两人死亡、四人受伤。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:47:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/two-killed-explosion-chemical-plant-chinas-ningxia-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>摩根士丹利表示，美元的主导储备货币地位将持续下去</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollars-dominant-reserve-currency-status-endure-says-morgan-stanley-2024-04-18/</link><description>摩根士丹利周四在一份报告中表示，美元的主导储备货币地位可能会持续下去，部分原因是即使是最受关注的替代货币人民币也无法成为可信的挑战者。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:42:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollars-dominant-reserve-currency-status-endure-says-morgan-stanley-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>克拉克表示，阿斯顿·马丁曾担心阿隆索可能退出 F1</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/aston-martin-had-feared-alonso-might-quit-f1-says-krack-2024-04-18/</link><description>阿斯顿·马丁车队负责人迈克·克拉克周四表示，阿斯顿·马丁担心一级方程式 24 场比赛的强度可能会导致费尔南多·阿隆索就此结束，而不是续约至少两年。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:42:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/aston-martin-had-feared-alonso-might-quit-f1-says-krack-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>独家：墨西哥面临美国压力，将停止对中国电动汽车制造商的激励</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mexico-facing-us-pressure-will-halt-incentives-chinese-ev-makers-2024-04-18/</link><description>三名知情墨西哥官员表示，在美国的压力下，墨西哥联邦政府拒绝为电动汽车生产投资提供低成本公共土地或减税等激励措施，与中国汽车制造商保持一定距离。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:18:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mexico-facing-us-pressure-will-halt-incentives-chinese-ev-makers-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：随着科技盈利的临近，石油和美元的反弹播下了平静的种子</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-18/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 10:04:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>小米称其电动汽车销量比预期高3-5倍</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-says-sales-its-new-ev-have-been-3-5-times-higher-than-expected-2024-04-18/</link><description>小米首席执行官雷军周四表示，中国智能手机制造商小米首款电动汽车的销量比预期高出 3-5 倍，该公司开始提前向买家交付所谓的 SU7 的标准版本。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 09:50:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-says-sales-its-new-ev-have-been-3-5-times-higher-than-expected-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>塞尔维亚村庄里最后的妇女被我的吞噬了</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/last-women-standing-serbian-village-swallowed-by-mine-2024-04-18/</link><description>这些妇女包括护士、学校教师、学生和家庭主妇。他们跨越了三代人。他们已经做好了战斗的准备。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 09:34:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/last-women-standing-serbian-village-swallowed-by-mine-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>在塞尔维亚村庄，妇女们奋力逃离侵占的地雷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbian-village-women-fight-escape-encroaching-mine-2024-04-18/</link><description>黎明前，78 岁的武科萨瓦·拉迪沃耶维奇 (Vukosava Radivojevic) 为丈夫准备了早餐，然后走进塞尔维亚东部的村庄，守卫路障，阻止卡车进入露天铜矿，居民称该铜矿污染了当地的土地和水源。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 08:58:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/serbian-village-women-fight-escape-encroaching-mine-2024-04-18/</guid></item><item><title>紧张局势升温之际，中国外交部欢迎布林肯访华</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-foreign-ministry-welcomes-blinkens-visit-china-tensions-simmer-2024-04-18/</link><description>中国外交部周四欢迎美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯访华，两国因全球贸易、地区冲突和俄罗斯-乌克兰战争而紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 08:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-foreign-ministry-welcomes-blinkens-visit-china-tensions-simmer-2024-04-18/</guid></item></channel></rss>